(1707, 'Trophy hunting', 'negatively impacts ecosystem', 'Testimony', 'Enter Example', 'Enter URL', 'Enter Reason Property', 1, 'Enter timestamp of specified material', ', Trophy hunting may cause extinction in a changing environment, ScienceDaily, November 28, 2018', '\"Trophy hunting and other activities involving the targeting of high-quality male animals could lead to the extinction of certain species faced with changing environmental conditions, according to new research.\"', '2022-04-16 03:42:36', 'support', 23, 'supporting', 1706, NULL, 0),
